description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 1 of 4 of the live May matchup between Team Ice and The Pirates.
It's Ariel X (last season's champion) and Mellanie Monroe up against Dia Zerva and Jessie Coxx. Both teams have suffered a loss and neither can afford a second!
This first round was a barn burner - both teams going all out in the first round to capture the lead. Great one-on-one action between Ariel and Dia. Which team wants this win more? Which girl is going to step up and be the hero? All this action was shot in front of a live audience. Nothing scripted. Pure brutal combat.
title: ROUND ONE: Team Ice (0-1) vs The Pirates (0-1)
